cu.explanation_en: Setting the AMF IP address to an unreachable IP '10.0.0.1' will cause routing failure and prevent proper AMF connection.

du.explanation_en: Setting DL-UL transmission periodicity to 0 (out of range) will cause timing misalignment and lead to transmission scheduling failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 DL-UL 傳輸週期設定為 0（超出範圍）會導致時序錯位，並造成傳輸排程失敗。
